OOC: First of all Kinger, theres no need to shout.  And now for everyone, a 
few months ago my e-mail started screwing up. It never fully fixed, but i 
read the message board to find out the mails ive been missing. In other 
words, just because your mail didnt reach my mailbox does not mean i havent 
read it. I hope that staightens things out.
